{'applicant': 'Bianca Moretti', 'email': 'bmoretti09@gmail.com', 'status': 'waitlisted'}

Should she write a letter of continued interest or move on?

One line from the district export CSV-to-JSON job:

{"sid": "S-221487", "student": "Caleb Osei", "advisor": "R. Feldstein"}

The sid is what the district uses on all his records. Does our plan sync need it?

The form autosave dumped this half-broken snippet when her browser crashed:

{student: "Fiona Gallagher-Reyes", city: "El Paso", grade: 10,}

Can we recover her intake from it or does mom need to redo the form?

